Detailed Description

cvmx_srio::_asmbly_info

The Assembly Info register controls the assembly revision visible in the ASSY_REV field of the SRIOMAINT()_ASMBLY_INFO register. This register is only reset during COLD boot and may only be modified while SRIO()_STATUS_REG[ACCESS] is zero.

This register is reset by the coprocessor-clock cold reset.
